@startuml sequence_auth
title Diagrammes de Séquence — Authentification (Inscription & Connexion)

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #7C3AED
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #7C3AED
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #EDE7F6
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #7C3AED
skinparam sequenceActorBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
skinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #7C3AED
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam NoteBorderColor #FBC02D
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #5B21B6
skinparam sequenceGroupHeaderFontColor #5B21B6

actor "Utilisateur" as User
participant "Navigateur\n(Next.js)" as Browser
participant "Next.js\nMiddleware" as MW
participant "Page SignIn\n/ SignUp" as Page
participant "API Client\n(lib/api.ts)" as API
participant "Fastify\n(Auth Routes)" as Auth
participant "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "JWT Service\n(lib/jwt.ts)" as JWT
participant "bcrypt" as Bcrypt

' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' SCENARIO 1 — INSCRIPTION (Register)
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Scénario 1 : Inscription (Sign Up) ==

User -> Browser : Navigue vers /signup
Browser -> MW : GET /signup
MW -> MW : Vérifie cookie morph_token
note right of MW : Cookie absent → chemin public\n→ NextResponse.next()
MW --> Browser : 200 OK (page autorisée)
Browser -> Page : Rend SignUpPage

User -> Page : Saisit email + password + confirm
User -> Page : Clique "Create account"
Page -> Page : Valide:\n- passwords match\n- length ≥ 6

Page -> API : register(email, password)
API -> Auth : POST /api/auth/register\n{email, password}\ncredentials: 'include'

Auth -> Auth : Valide email + password\n(non vide, longueur ≥ 6)

Auth -> DB : SELECT id FROM morph_users\nWHERE email = $1
DB --> Auth : [] (aucun résultat)

Auth -> Bcrypt : hash(password, salt=12)
Bcrypt --> Auth : passwordHash

Auth -> DB : INSERT INTO morph_users\n(email, password_hash)\nRETURNING id, email
DB --> Auth : {id: 1, email: "..."}

Auth -> JWT : signToken({userId: 1, email})
JWT --> Auth : token (expire dans 7j)

Auth --> API : HTTP 201\nSet-Cookie: morph_token=<jwt>; httpOnly\n{user: {id: 1, email}}
API --> Page : {user}

Page -> Browser : router.push('/')
Browser -> MW : GET /
MW -> MW : Détecte cookie morph_token ✓
MW --> Browser : 200 OK
Browser -> User : Affiche le workspace (canvas)

' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' SCENARIO 2 — CONNEXION (Sign In)
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Scénario 2 : Connexion (Sign In) ==

User -> Browser : Navigue vers /signin
Browser -> MW : GET /signin
MW -> MW : Cookie absent → chemin public → next()
MW --> Browser : 200 OK
Browser -> Page : Rend SignInPage

User -> Page : Saisit email + password
User -> Page : Clique "Sign in"

Page -> API : login(email, password)
API -> Auth : POST /api/auth/login\n{email, password}\ncredentials: 'include'

Auth -> DB : SELECT id, email, password_hash\nFROM morph_users\nWHERE email = $1
DB --> Auth : {id, email, passwordHash}

Auth -> Bcrypt : compare(password, passwordHash)
Bcrypt --> Auth : true ✓

Auth -> JWT : signToken({userId, email})
JWT --> Auth : token

Auth --> API : HTTP 200\nSet-Cookie: morph_token=<jwt>; httpOnly; SameSite=Lax\n{user: {id, email}}
API --> Page : {user}

Page -> Browser : router.push('/')
Browser -> MW : GET /
MW --> Browser : 200 OK (cookie présent)
Browser -> User : Affiche le workspace

' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' SCENARIO 3 — ERREUR D'AUTHENTIFICATION
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Scénario 3 : Connexion échouée (mauvais mot de passe) ==

User -> Page : Saisit email + mauvais password
Page -> API : login(email, wrongPassword)
API -> Auth : POST /api/auth/login

Auth -> DB : SELECT ... WHERE email = $1
DB --> Auth : {id, email, passwordHash}

Auth -> Bcrypt : compare(wrongPassword, hash)
Bcrypt --> Auth : false ✗

Auth --> API : HTTP 401\n{error: "Invalid email or password"}
API --> Page : throw Error("API 401: ...")
Page -> Page : Affiche message d'erreur\n"Invalid email or password"
Page --> User : ❌ Formulaire avec erreur

' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' SCENARIO 4 — DÉCONNEXION (Sign Out)
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Scénario 4 : Déconnexion (Sign Out) ==

User -> Browser : Clique "Sign out" (Sidebar)
Browser -> API : logout()
API -> Auth : POST /api/auth/logout\ncredentials: 'include'
Auth -> Auth : clearCookie('morph_token')
Auth --> API : HTTP 200 {ok: true}\nSet-Cookie: morph_token=; Max-Age=0

API --> Browser : {ok: true}
Browser -> Browser : window.location.href = '/signin'
Browser -> MW : GET /signin
MW -> MW : Cookie effacé → chemin public → next()
MW --> Browser : 200 OK
Browser -> User : Affiche la page de connexion

note over JWT : Algorithme : HS256\nExpiration : 7 jours\nSecret : JWT_SECRET (env var)\nStockage : httpOnly cookie\n(inaccessible depuis JS)

@enduml
